  "title": "🤩FEB START🤩 Fun Events Executive- Fresh grad welcome/ travelling opportunities!",
  "description": "<p><strong>WHAT ARE YOU MOTIVATED BY?</strong><br>\n<br>\n- High Paying Jobs?<br>\n- Regular trips?<br>\n- Have fun with colleagues and peers when working<br>\n- Great examples to learn from<br>\n- Working for a good cause<br>\n- Learning versatile skills for your future<br>\n<br>\nIf any of the above mentioned interest you, we are hiring people who are in search of one of these.<br>\n<br>\nJOB OVERVIEW<br>\n<br>\n- Office hours, 5.5days/week<br>\n- Tech savvy and fast in picking up new skills<br>\n- Outstanding interpersonal and communication skills<br>\n- Meeting customers out of office daily in events and corporate settings<br>\n- Discover unconventional ways to improve and excel<br>\n- Based in Singapore<br>\n<br>\nNow click \"Apply\"! Please be aware that only those who make the shortlist will receive a call within three business days.</p>",
